headline: PulteGroup Initiates Strategic Expansion into Cincinnati Market
summary: ATLANTA, November 17, 2025--Building on its longstanding success in the cities of Cleveland and Columbus, PulteGroup, Inc. (NYSE: PHM), the nation's third largest homebuilder, announces its plans to enter the Cincinnati market.
